today  i will be learing about data types and manipulation using data types 

todays project was about writing a tip calculator ]
 code 
 print("Welcome to the tip calculator.")
bill = float(input("what was the total bill: "))
# print(bill)
percentage = int(input("what percentage tip would you like to give? 10, 12 or 15: "))
people = int(input("How many Peopel to split the bill?: "))
new_percent = percentage / 100 * bill
# print(new_percent)
new_bill = bill + new_percent
# print(new_bill)
bill_per_person = round(new_bill/people, 2)
final_amount = "{:.2f}".format(bill_per_person)
# print(bill_per_person)
print(f"Each person should pay  {final_amount}")
